u play! The town evolves over time and unlocks new features to use on your next run.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
